thread.title: Tim Mullis
thread.title_full: 42nd Street Photo reviewed by Tim Mullis

author: Tim Mullis
title: Tim Mullis
text:
I just bought a Nikon AF-S DX 55-300 / 4.5-5.6G ED VR Nikkor Lens for my Nikon D5100. 42nd Street Photo had the best price I could find on the internet, called me the morning I ordered it asking about a delivery option, shipped it that day, and it was received two days after I ordered it
! This was my first experience with 42nd Street Photo, but it will not be my last. Great job guys!!
